section {
    head {
        0,
        "Writings",
    },
    par {
        'I write things on a variety of topics that interest me.
Many software engineers have blogs with software engineering stuff on there.
There will be some pages on software but also on very unrelated things.
This is also not a blog.
The structure is not linear and each page may evolve and update as time goes.
At any time, the page reflects what I think of something or what I thought of something when I
last wrote about that something.',
    },
    section {
        head {
            0,
            "Pages",
        },
        par {
            'There are but a few pages for now:',
        },
